@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #FF0000, #FFA500, #FFFF00, #008000, #0000FF, #4B0082, #EE82EE);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        main {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }

        p {
            margin: 0 0 20px;
        }

        /* Team Section */
        .team-member {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            width: 200px;
            vertical-align: top;
            margin: 0 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Add a shadow effect */
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease; /* Add smooth transition for hover effect */
        }

            .team-member img {
                border-radius: 50%;
                width: 150px;
                height: 150px;
                object-fit: cover;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                transition: transform 0.3s ease; /* Add smooth transition for hover effect */
            }

            .team-member:hover img {
                transform: scale(1.1); /* Slightly enlarge the image on hover */
            }

            .team-member:hover {
                transform: translateY(-10px); /* Slightly move the card up on hover */
                box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2); /* Enhance the shadow effect on hover */
            }

        footer {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <p>Welcome to our company! We take pride of our enduring reputation for providing exceptional goods in a range of categories, such as wall decor, furniture, lighting, mirrors, and art. Our devotion to delivering exceptional customer service is the only thing that can match our commitment to perfection. Get in touch with us right now to learn how we can assist you in locating the ideal mirror for your requirements.</p>
        <p>Founded in 2024, we have consistently strived to innovate and improve our offerings to ensure customer satisfaction.</p>

        <h2>Team Members</h2><br />
        <div class="team-member">
            <alt="Team Member 1" />
            <h3>Vandan Patel</h3>
            <p>CEO & Founder</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
            <alt="Team Member 2" />
            <h3>Divyansh Solanki</h3>
            <p>Chief Operating Officer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
            <alt="Team Member 3" />
            <h3>Nidhi Nidhi</h3>
            <p>Chief Technology Officer</p>
        </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Our Company. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
